[
  {
    "speaker": "char_lin_zhen_nan",
    "speaker_name": "林震南",
    "listener": "char_lin_ping_zhi",
    "text": "平儿，好教你得知，咱们镖局子今儿得到了一个喜讯。",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 28,
    "line_end": 28
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lin_ping_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "林平之",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "什么东西！两个不带眼的狗崽子，却到我们福州府来撒野！",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 45,
    "line_end": 45
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lin_ping_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "林平之",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "史⋯⋯史镖头，那⋯⋯那怎么办？我本来⋯⋯本来没想杀他。",
    "tone": "恐惧",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 83,
    "line_end": 83
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lin_zhen_nan",
    "speaker_name": "林震南",
    "listener": "char_lin_ping_zhi",
    "text": "江湖上如遇到了劲敌，应变竟也这等迟钝，你这条肩膀还在么？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 97,
    "line_end": 97
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lin_zhen_nan",
    "speaker_name": "林震南",
    "listener": "char_lin_ping_zhi",
    "text": "你曾祖远图公创下七十二路辟邪剑法，当年威震江湖，当真说得上打遍天下无敌手。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 97,
    "line_end": 97
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lao_de_nuo",
    "speaker_name": "劳德诺",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "师父信中说，现下已将两名顽徒重重责打，原当命其亲上青城，负荆请罪。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 2,
    "line_start": 304,
    "line_end": 304
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yue_bu_qun",
    "speaker_name": "岳不群",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "德诺，你入我门之前，已在江湖上闯荡多年，可曾听得武林之中，对福威镖局总镖头林震南的武功，如何评论？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 3,
    "line_start": 2,
    "line_end": 2
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yue_bu_qun",
    "speaker_name": "岳不群",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "是了！福威镖局这些年来兴旺发达，倒是江湖上朋友给面子的居多。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 3,
    "line_start": 4,
    "line_end": 4
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ding_yi",
    "speaker_name": "定逸",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "令狐冲这小子一张臭嘴，不知是那个缺德之人调教出来的。",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 20,
    "line_end": 20
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_liu_zheng_feng",
    "speaker_name": "刘正风",
    "listener": "char_ding_yi",
    "text": "令狐师侄若不是看重恒山派，华山派自岳先生而下，若不都是心中敬重佩服三位师太，他又怎肯如此尽心竭力的相救贵派弟子？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 22,
    "line_end": 22
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_tian_bo_guang",
    "speaker_name": "田伯光",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我田伯光独往独来，横行天下，那里能顾忌得这么多？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 26,
    "line_end": 26
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yi_lin",
    "speaker_name": "仪琳",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "这位令狐师兄于我有救命大恩，终于为我而死，我⋯⋯我不配做他朋友。",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 3,
    "line_end": 3
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_qu_fei_yan",
    "speaker_name": "曲非烟",
    "listener": "char_yi_lin",
    "text": "姊姊，你生得这般美貌，剃了光头便大大减色，倘若留起一头乌油油的长发，那才叫好看呢。",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 19,
    "line_end": 19
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_qu_fei_yan",
    "speaker_name": "曲非烟",
    "listener": "char_tian_bo_guang",
    "text": "田伯光，你师父在这里，快快过来磕头！",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 49,
    "line_end": 49
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_tian_bo_guang",
    "speaker_name": "田伯光",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "什么师父？小娘皮胡说八道，我撕烂你臭嘴。",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 49,
    "line_end": 49
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yu_cang_hai",
    "speaker_name": "余沧海",
    "listener": "char_ling_hu_chong",
    "text": "你便是令狐冲了？好，好！你在这妓院里，干什么来着？",
    "tone": "嘲讽",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 182,
    "line_end": 182
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ling_hu_chong",
    "speaker_name": "令狐冲",
    "listener": "char_yu_cang_hai",
    "text": "这叫做明知故问。在妓院之中，还干什么来着？",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 182,
    "line_end": 182
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yue_bu_qun",
    "speaker_name": "岳不群",
    "listener": "char_mu_gao_feng",
    "text": "木兄，怎地跟孩子们一般见识？我说你倒是返老还童了。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 310,
    "line_end": 310
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fei_bin",
    "speaker_name": "费彬",
    "listener": "char_liu_zheng_feng",
    "text": "刘正风和魔教妖人结交，意欲不利我五岳剑派。",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 126,
    "line_end": 126
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_liu_zheng_feng",
    "speaker_name": "刘正风",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "刘某结交朋友，乃是刘某自己的事，跟五岳剑派有什么相干？",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 130,
    "line_end": 130
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ding_yi",
    "speaker_name": "定逸",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "刘贤弟，你不用耽心，天下事抬不过一个'理'字。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 130,
    "line_end": 130
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_mo_da",
    "speaker_name": "莫大先生",
    "listener": "char_fei_bin",
    "text": "该杀！",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 142,
    "line_end": 142
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yue_bu_qun",
    "speaker_name": "岳不群",
    "listener": "char_ling_hu_chong",
    "text": "冲儿，你就是口齿轻薄，说话没点正经，怎能作众师弟、师妹的表率？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 282,
    "line_end": 282
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ling_hu_chong",
    "speaker_name": "令狐冲",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "余矮子的剑法，可比师父差得远了，斗到后来，他只好三十六着。青城派屁股向后、逃之夭夭的功夫，原比别派为高。",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 282,
    "line_end": 282
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yue_bu_qun",
    "speaker_name": "岳不群",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我华山派向来的宗旨是'人不犯我，我不犯人'，除了跟魔教是死对头之外，与武林中各门各派均无嫌隙。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 320,
    "line_end": 320
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yue_bu_qun",
    "speaker_name": "岳不群",
    "listener": "char_ling_hu_chong",
    "text": "你是本门大弟子，我和你师娘对你期望甚殷，盼你他日能为我们分任艰巨，抵挡祸患，光大华山一派。但你牵缠于儿女私情，不求上进，荒废武功，可令我们失望得很了。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 9,
    "line_start": 18,
    "line_end": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_feng_qing_yang",
    "speaker_name": "风清扬",
    "listener": "char_ling_hu_chong",
    "text": "令狐冲你这小子，实在也太不成器！我来教你。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 10,
    "line_start": 9,
    "line_end": 9
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_feng_qing_yang",
    "speaker_name": "风清扬",
    "listener": "char_ling_hu_chong",
    "text": "剑术之道，讲究如行云流水，任意所之。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 10,
    "line_start": 13,
    "line_end": 13
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_feng_qing_yang",
    "speaker_name": "风清扬",
    "listener": "char_ling_hu_chong",
    "text": "活学活使，只是第一步。要做到出手无招，那才真是踏入了高手的境界。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 10,
    "line_start": 65,
    "line_end": 65
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_feng_qing_yang",
    "speaker_name": "风清扬",
    "listener": "char_ling_hu_chong",
    "text": "根本无招，如何可破？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 10,
    "line_start": 67,
    "line_end": 67
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_feng_qing_yang",
    "speaker_name": "风清扬",
    "listener": "char_ling_hu_chong",
    "text": "招数是死的，发招之人却是活的。死招数破得再妙，遇上了活招数，免不了缚手缚脚，只有任人屠戮。这个'活'字，你要牢牢记住了。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 10,
    "line_start": 59,
    "line_end": 59
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_feng_qing_yang",
    "speaker_name": "风清扬",
    "listener": "char_ling_hu_chong",
    "text": "五岳剑派中各有无数蠢才，以为将师父传下来的剑招学得精熟，自然而然便成高手，哼哼，熟读唐诗三百首，不会作诗也会吟！",
    "tone": "嘲讽",
    "chapter": 10,
    "line_start": 63,
    "line_end": 63
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_feng_bu_ping",
    "speaker_name": "封不平",
    "listener": "char_yue_bu_qun",
    "text": "是你师父，那是不错，是不是华山派掌门，却要走着瞧了。",
    "tone": "嘲讽",
    "chapter": 11,
    "line_start": 46,
    "line_end": 46
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yue_bu_qun",
    "speaker_name": "岳不群",
    "listener": "char_feng_bu_ping",
    "text": "五岳剑派都使剑，那固然不错，可是不论那一门、那一派，都讲究'以气驭剑'之道。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 11,
    "line_start": 48,
    "line_end": 48
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ling_hu_chong",
    "speaker_name": "令狐冲",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "师父、师娘和众师弟、师妹不感激我救了他们性命，反而人人大有疑忌之意⋯⋯原来他们都认定我吞没了林震南的辟邪剑谱。",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 13,
    "line_start": 6,
    "line_end": 6
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ren_ying_ying",
    "speaker_name": "任盈盈",
    "listener": "char_ling_hu_chong",
    "text": "你学琴之时，须得心中空灵澄澈，不可有半分杂念。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 14,
    "line_start": 50,
    "line_end": 50
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fang_zheng",
    "speaker_name": "方证大师",
    "listener": "char_ling_hu_chong",
    "text": "少侠须得投我嵩山少林寺门下，为少林派俗家弟子。少侠若不嫌弃，便归老衲门下，为'国'字辈弟子，可更名为令狐国冲。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 18,
    "line_start": 82,
    "line_end": 82
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_xiang_wen_tian",
    "speaker_name": "向问天",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "不错，这是吸星大法，那一位有兴致的便上来试试。",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 18,
    "line_start": 380,
    "line_end": 380
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ren_wo_xing",
    "speaker_name": "任我行",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "千秋万载，一统江湖！",
    "tone": "激动",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line_start": 60,
    "line_end": 60
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_hei_bai_zi",
    "speaker_name": "黑白子",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "任⋯⋯任老爷子⋯⋯你⋯⋯你的吸星大法⋯⋯",
    "tone": "恐惧",
    "chapter": 21,
    "line_start": 254,
    "line_end": 254
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ren_wo_xing",
    "speaker_name": "任我行",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "当世武林之中，要找一位比方证大师更合式的掌门人，那是谁也没法子了。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 27,
    "line_start": 276,
    "line_end": 276
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fang_zheng",
    "speaker_name": "方证大师",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "左盟主文才武略，确是武林中的杰出人物，五岳剑派之中，原本没第二人比得上。不过他抱负太大，急欲压倒武当、少林两派，未免有些不择手段。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 30,
    "line_start": 22,
    "line_end": 22
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_chong_xu",
    "speaker_name": "冲虚道长",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "一个门派创建成名，那是数百年来无数英雄豪杰，花了无数心血累积而成。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 30,
    "line_start": 28,
    "line_end": 28
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_dong_fang_bu_bai",
    "speaker_name": "东方不败",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我练那《葵花宝典》，余下的时间便绣花。我生平最喜好的便是绣花。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 31,
    "line_start": 78,
    "line_end": 78
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_tong_bai_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "童百熊",
    "listener": "char_dong_fang_bu_bai",
    "text": "东方兄弟，这几年来，我要见你一面也难。你隐居起来，苦练《葵花宝典》，可知不知道教中故旧星散，大祸便在眉睫吗？",
    "tone": "焦急",
    "chapter": 31,
    "line_start": 78,
    "line_end": 78
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ling_hu_chong",
    "speaker_name": "令狐冲",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "人生在世，会当畅情适意，连酒也不能喝，还活着干什么？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 33,
    "line_start": 288,
    "line_end": 288
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ren_ying_ying",
    "speaker_name": "任盈盈",
    "listener": "char_ling_hu_chong",
    "text": "冲哥，你是在找我吗？",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 33,
    "line_start": 82,
    "line_end": 82
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zuo_leng_chan",
    "speaker_name": "左冷禅",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "岳姑娘精通泰山、衡山、恒山三派剑法，确是难能可贵，若能以嵩山剑法胜得我手中长剑，我嵩山全派自当奉岳先生为掌门。",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 34,
    "line_start": 4,
    "line_end": 4
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yue_bu_qun",
    "speaker_name": "岳不群",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "华山门下众人听着：我和左师兄是切磋武艺，绝无仇怨，倘若左师兄失手杀了我，或者打得我身受重伤，大伙儿不可对左师伯怀恨。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 34,
    "line_start": 106,
    "line_end": 106
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yue_bu_qun",
    "speaker_name": "岳不群",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "在下的武功剑法，比之少林派方证大师、武当派冲虚道长，以及丐帮解帮主诸位前辈英雄，那可望尘莫及。",
    "tone": "嘲讽",
    "chapter": 34,
    "line_start": 76,
    "line_end": 76
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lin_ping_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "林平之",
    "listener": "char_yue_ling_shan",
    "text": "你爹爹做这种事，就不难听？他做得，我便说不得？",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 35,
    "line_start": 482,
    "line_end": 482
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yue_ling_shan",
    "speaker_name": "岳灵珊",
    "listener": "char_lin_ping_zhi",
    "text": "大师哥气量大得很，从小就不贪图旁人的物事。爹爹说他取了你的剑谱，我一直有点怀疑。",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 35,
    "line_start": 482,
    "line_end": 482
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ling_hu_chong",
    "speaker_name": "令狐冲",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "小师妹或许喜欢人家叫她林夫人。",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 36,
    "line_start": 194,
    "line_end": 194
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ren_ying_ying",
    "speaker_name": "任盈盈",
    "listener": "char_ling_hu_chong",
    "text": "林平之如此无情无义，岳姑娘泉下有灵，明白了他的歹毒心肠，不会愿作林夫人了。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 36,
    "line_start": 194,
    "line_end": 194
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ren_ying_ying",
    "speaker_name": "任盈盈",
    "listener": "char_ling_hu_chong",
    "text": "咱们便在这里住些时候，一面养伤，一面伴坟。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 36,
    "line_start": 202,
    "line_end": 202
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ren_wo_xing",
    "speaker_name": "任我行",
    "listener": "char_ling_hu_chong",
    "text": "令狐掌门，且请一旁就座。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 39,
    "line_start": 180,
    "line_end": 180
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ling_hu_chong",
    "speaker_name": "令狐冲",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "大丈夫行事，爱怎样便怎样，行云流水，任意所之，什么武林规矩，门派教条，全都是放他妈的狗臭屁！",
    "tone": "激动",
    "chapter": 39,
    "line_start": 186,
    "line_end": 186
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fang_zheng",
    "speaker_name": "方证大师",
    "listener": "char_ling_hu_chong",
    "text": "令狐掌门此言差矣。魔教要毁我少林、武当与五岳剑派，百余年前便已存此心，其时老衲都未出世，跟令狐掌门又有何干？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 40,
    "line_start": 23,
    "line_end": 23
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fang_zheng",
    "speaker_name": "方证大师",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "一统江湖，既无可能，亦非众人之福。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 40,
    "line_start": 27,
    "line_end": 27
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ling_hu_chong",
    "speaker_name": "令狐冲",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "晚辈只要一听到什么'圣教主'，什么'千秋万载，一统江湖'，全身便起鸡皮疙瘩。",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 40,
    "line_start": 53,
    "line_end": 53
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ling_hu_chong",
    "speaker_name": "令狐冲",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "今日得聆大师指点，真如瞎子开了眼一般，就算以后没日子修练，也一样的欢喜。",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 40,
    "line_start": 69,
    "line_end": 69
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fang_zheng",
    "speaker_name": "方证大师",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "任教主既说一个月之内，要将恒山之上杀得鸡犬不留。他言出如山，决无更改。现下少林、武当、昆仑、峨嵋、崆峒各派好手，都已聚集在恒山脚下了。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 40,
    "line_start": 31,
    "line_end": 31
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fang_zheng",
    "speaker_name": "方证大师",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "听说日月教中有句话，说道是'千秋万载，一统江湖'，既存此心，武林中如何更有宁日？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 40,
    "line_start": 27,
    "line_end": 27
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_chong_xu",
    "speaker_name": "冲虚道长",
    "listener": "char_ling_hu_chong",
    "text": "令狐兄弟，我带他们二人来，另有一番用意。盼望他们二人能给咱们办一件大事。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 40,
    "line_start": 87,
    "line_end": 87
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ling_hu_chong",
    "speaker_name": "令狐冲",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "任教主见到这张宝椅，非上去坐一下不可。椅中机簧发作，便可送了他性命，是不是？",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 40,
    "line_start": 97,
    "line_end": 97
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ling_hu_chong",
    "speaker_name": "令狐冲",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "五岳剑派，同气连枝，华山派也好，恒山派也好，都是你这淫贼的对头⋯⋯",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 8,
    "line_start": 242,
    "line_end": 242
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_tian_bo_guang",
    "speaker_name": "田伯光",
    "listener": "char_ling_hu_chong",
    "text": "令狐兄，你得风老前辈指点诀窍之后，果然剑法大进，不过适才给你点倒，乃一时疏忽，田某心中不服，咱们再来比过。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 12,
    "line_start": 89,
    "line_end": 89
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ling_hu_chong",
    "speaker_name": "令狐冲",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "难道我十多年来所练内功，竟一点也没剩下？",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 12,
    "line_start": 312,
    "line_end": 312
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fang_sheng",
    "speaker_name": "方生大师",
    "listener": "char_ling_hu_chong",
    "text": "你⋯⋯你⋯⋯",
    "tone": "激动",
    "chapter": 16,
    "line_start": 356,
    "line_end": 356
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ling_hu_chong",
    "speaker_name": "令狐冲",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "风太师叔待弟子恩德如山。",
    "tone": "激动",
    "chapter": 17,
    "line_start": 356,
    "line_end": 356
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_zhong_gong",
    "speaker_name": "黄钟公",
    "listener": "char_ling_hu_chong",
    "text": "风兄弟，我指点你一条路子，对方肯不肯答允，却是难言。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 20,
    "line_start": 108,
    "line_end": 108
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ling_hu_chong",
    "speaker_name": "令狐冲",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我这一刀怎地如此快法？手刚伸出，刀鞘已戳中了他咽喉要害？",
    "tone": "激动",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line_start": 368,
    "line_end": 368
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yue_ling_shan",
    "speaker_name": "岳灵珊",
    "listener": "char_ling_hu_chong",
    "text": "大师哥，你⋯⋯你别这样。",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 24,
    "line_start": 50,
    "line_end": 50
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_mo_da",
    "speaker_name": "莫大先生",
    "listener": "char_ling_hu_chong",
    "text": "你后来怎地却好了？是修习了少林派《易筋经》神功，是不是？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 25,
    "line_start": 308,
    "line_end": 308
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ling_hu_chong",
    "speaker_name": "令狐冲",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "令狐冲拜见两位老人家。",
    "tone": "恳求",
    "chapter": 26,
    "line_start": 122,
    "line_end": 122
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yue_bu_qun",
    "speaker_name": "岳不群",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "是左冷禅害的，那又如何？你如拿到了证据，便当邀集正教中的英雄，齐向左冷禅问罪。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 28,
    "line_start": 128,
    "line_end": 128
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fang_zheng",
    "speaker_name": "方证大师",
    "listener": "char_ling_hu_chong",
    "text": "令狐掌门，今日嵩山派的丁老师率众前来，为的是什么？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 29,
    "line_start": 16,
    "line_end": 16
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ling_hu_chong",
    "speaker_name": "令狐冲",
    "listener": "char_fang_zheng",
    "text": "他传达左盟主的号令，不许晚辈接任恒山派掌门。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 29,
    "line_start": 16,
    "line_end": 16
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ren_wo_xing",
    "speaker_name": "任我行",
    "listener": "char_dong_fang_bu_bai",
    "text": "东方兄弟，你练这《葵花宝典》，可知已是走火入魔了么？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 31,
    "line_start": 81,
    "line_end": 81
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ling_hu_chong",
    "speaker_name": "令狐冲",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "他⋯⋯他⋯⋯要我加盟日月神教，我⋯⋯我不肯⋯⋯",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 37,
    "line_start": 50,
    "line_end": 50
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ren_wo_xing",
    "speaker_name": "任我行",
    "listener": "char_ling_hu_chong",
    "text": "你如不肯加盟日月神教，我不来勉强你，但恒山派上下，鸡犬不留。",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 37,
    "line_start": 52,
    "line_end": 52
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ren_ying_ying",
    "speaker_name": "任盈盈",
    "listener": "char_ling_hu_chong",
    "text": "冲哥，你⋯⋯你别答应他⋯⋯",
    "tone": "恳求",
    "chapter": 37,
    "line_start": 54,
    "line_end": 54
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yue_bu_qun",
    "speaker_name": "岳不群",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "众位英雄，今日五岳并派，岳某侥幸⋯⋯",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 38,
    "line_start": 44,
    "line_end": 44
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ling_hu_chong",
    "speaker_name": "令狐冲",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "辟邪剑法，剑术至尊。先练剑气，再练剑神⋯⋯",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 38,
    "line_start": 44,
    "line_end": 44
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ling_hu_chong",
    "speaker_name": "令狐冲",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "原来她⋯⋯她便是日月神教的圣姑⋯⋯",
    "tone": "激动",
    "chapter": 15,
    "line_start": 50,
    "line_end": 50
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ren_ying_ying",
    "speaker_name": "任盈盈",
    "listener": "char_ling_hu_chong",
    "text": "你⋯⋯你别走⋯⋯",
    "tone": "恳求",
    "chapter": 15,
    "line_start": 52,
    "line_end": 52
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_zhong_gong",
    "speaker_name": "黄钟公",
    "listener": "char_ling_hu_chong",
    "text": "风兄弟，你琴艺高超，老夫佩服。",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 19,
    "line_start": 50,
    "line_end": 50
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ling_hu_chong",
    "speaker_name": "令狐冲",
    "listener": "char_huang_zhong_gong",
    "text": "前辈谬赞，晚辈愧不敢当。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 19,
    "line_start": 52,
    "line_end": 52
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_tian_men",
    "speaker_name": "天门道人",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "忠于泰山派的弟子们，今日咱们死战到底，血溅嵩山。",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 32,
    "line_start": 122,
    "line_end": 122
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zuo_leng_chan",
    "speaker_name": "左冷禅",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "五岳剑派合而为一，乃是大势所趋，谁也不能阻挡。",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 32,
    "line_start": 8,
    "line_end": 8
  }
]